"name": "FAIR-Checker",
"description": "FAIR-Checker is a web and command-line tool to assess FAIR principles and help data providers improve the quality of their digital resources. It extracts embedded metadata (RDFa, JSON-LD, microdata), evaluates FAIR metrics, and provides recommendations and inspection tools.",
